"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-03-08-PARIS-2024-OLYMPICS-OPENING-CEREMONY-TO-START-AT-7-30-P-M-LOCAL-TIME-1830-GMT-ORGANISERS-1rOfN0V4Z3y-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  The Paris 2024 Olympics opening ceremony will start at 7:30 p.m. local time, organizers said on Friday as they gear up for the final straight before the Games.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We chose that time to make the most of the light,\\\" Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet told a press conference following the seventh and final Coordination Commission with the International Olympic Committee (IOC).\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.071806091138616e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony, a six-kilometer parade along the River Seine attended by more than 300,000, will take place on July 26, when the sun sets at 9:35 p.m. local time.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Participants attend a free sport session as part of the 'Le 3 Mars, les sportives gagnent du terrain' ('On March 3, sportswomen gain ground') event, with the Arc de Triomphe in the background on the Champs Elysees avenue in Paris, France, March 3, 2024.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5166697144712158e-15, \"text\": \"Arc de Triomphe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\"}, {\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9918285953524741, \"rank\": 0.008238720428601937, \"text\": \"Champs Elysees\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0228746739028703e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999946704402787, \"rank\": 3.766042297676873e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  IOC Coordination Commission chairman Pierre-Olivier Beckers-Vieujant said he was confident Paris 2024 would be in position to deliver excellent Games.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3594602315866226e-26, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre-Olivier_Beckers-Vieujant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre-Olivier Beckers-Vieujant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre-Olivier_Beckers-Vieujant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre-Olivier_Beckers-Vieujant\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.071806091138616e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC Coordination Commission leaves Paris full of confidence that excellence is within reach,\\\" Beckers-Vieujant said.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3594602315866226e-26, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0228746739028703e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not see any challenge that could be an obstacle to the realization of the extraordinary vision that all the teams have had seven years ago (when Paris where awarded the 2024 Olympics).\\\"\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0228746739028703e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Games are just around the corner,\\\" he added, referring to the Olympic flame arriving from Greece in Marseille, southern France, in exactly two months.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9948515470730604, \"rank\": 0.00516800429973462, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9998995020753808, \"rank\": 0.00010050796169318138, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999946704402787, \"rank\": 3.766042297676873e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentenc